companyName: St. Augustine Gold and Copper Limited
description: St. Augustine Gold and Copper Limited, a mineral exploration company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and evaluation of mineral properties in the Philippines. It holds interests in the King-king copper-gold project that covers an area of approximately 1,548 hectares located in the Province of Compostela Valley, Mindanao Island. St. Augustine Gold and Copper Limited is headquartered in Singapore.
